y dislike:How she gets attached \nFears (And their causes):Losing those she loves \nAspirations:Must protect people \nEnergy (Energetic/Lazy/Etc):Lazy and loving\nOther/Extra:\n\nCharacter's Abilities\nCharacters Ability(s):time magic\nMechanics of Ability(s):it's very short time municipalities\nPassive/Non-Offensive Ability(s):she municipalities time space\n\nWeapon(s):Katana/ninja sword\nOther Items (Satchels, Bags, Etc):ninja satchel \n\nAdditional Information about Character\nVoice Claim:alluring \nRelatives (Parents, siblings, uncles/aunts, nieces/nephews):Tifa lockhart\nFriends:Hakari \nEnemies:Wolf\nFavorite Animal/Food/Song/Etc: wolf\u2019s,sushi,Hush\nEx-Significant Other:Wolf,Hakari,Wolfie\n\nBackstory:When she was a young Assassin she would sleep with her enemies and suck the life out of them then after she fell in love she trained herself to control her power and came up with a cure for her disease.\n\n\n==Music==\n* New, main vocalist of K-Pop group [[The Boyz (South Korean band)|The Boyz]]\n\n===Albums and EPs===\n* [[New (album)|''New'' (album)]], by Paul McCartney, 2013\n* [[New (EP)|''New'' (EP)]], by Regurgitator, 1995 \n\n===Songs===\n* [[New (Daya song)|\"New\" (Daya song)]], 2017\n* [[New (Paul McCartney song)|\"New\" (Paul McCartney song)]], 2013\n* [[New (No Doubt song)|\"New\" (No Doubt song)]], 1999\n*\"new\", by Loona from ''[[Yves (single album)|Yves]]'', 2017\n*\"The New\", by Interpol from ''[[Turn On the Bright Lights]]'', 2002\n\n== Acronyms ==\n* [[Net economic welfare]], a proposed macroeconomic indicator\n* [[Net explosive weight]], also known as net explosive quantity\n* [[Network of enlightened Women]], a conservative university women's organization\n* [[Next Entertainment World]], a South Korean film distribution company\n\n== Identification codes ==\n* [[Nepal Bhasa language]] ISO 639 language code\n* [[New Century Financial Corporation]] (NYSE stock abbreviation)\n* [[New Orleans Lakefront Airport]] (IATA airport code: NEW)\n* 